			<p>
				A folk concept album that plays like a short-film soundtrack, Mountain
				Bear's début full-length album Mountain Bear tells the story of a
				village making a hopeful go of a hard here and now. Pulling as much from
				their imaginations as from their encounters on the road, intimate
				moments give way to cinematic arrangements as characters emerge and
				speak through song.
			</p>
